title: The X-Files - Complete Set - Samples, Screenshots & Info
description:
Since TPB came back online, I have tried to add 
"The X-Files - Complete Set" here. It's already indexed on
several other public torrent sites. It seems it's not
possible, because the .torrent file is "too big" at over 
400 kilobytes, which  makes the TPB upload system reject it.

So here are samples, screenshots & info about the torrent,
as well as the .torrent file for starting the download.

Alternatively you can download the torrent from E-xtratorrent or
K-ickasstorrents.


SOME INFO ABOUT THE X-FILES - COMPLETE SET:

THE X-FILES - COMPLETE SET

The set includes:
* The X-Files (TV Series, 1993-2002)
* The X-Files: Fight The Future (Movie, 1998)
* The X-Files: I Want To Believe (Movie, 2008)
* The Lone Gunmen (Spin-Off TV Series, 2001)
* Extras for all of the above

File names ending with '+ C' denote optional
commentaries.

Also included:
* X-Files Comics
* X-Files Audiobooks
* X-Files E-books
* X-Files Soundtracks & misc X-files music
* The X-Files PC Game (1998)
